duties_responsibilities.duty: Generate and drive high-quality sales leads in the assigned geographical area.
Utilize a variety of mediums to generate new memberships, including nurturing productive relationships with senior citizens and partnering with external business partners.
Enroll new patients into medical centers by partnering with health agents, health brokers, and key local community partners.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or GED required, associate's or bachelor’s degree preferred.
